  <summary date="2018-06-21T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Reunite Children With Their Parents Act

This bill directs the Department of Homeland Security to reunite an alien who entered the United States with the alien's minor child (under the age of 18) who was separated from the child pending prosecution for improper entry or the adjudication of an asylum application.</summary>
